                Guide for the commands in GUIs:C
              ====================================

 These commands are used in various guis contained in the Gui4Cli
 archive. They are all pure and can be made resident. They are
 CLI commands - do not run them from the Workbench. Although they
 were writen for use with Gui4Cli, they can be used anywhere else
 too (like DirOpus, DM etc).

 CLI Commands :
 ===============

 @{" FSearch    " link "guis:g4c/fsearch/fsearch.readme/main"  } Lots of options - read them..
 @{" Rep        " link Rep      } FromFile/A,String/A,ToString/A,ToFile,I=Insensitive/S
 @{" Wrap       " link Wrap     } FILE/A,NEWFILE,L=LENGTH/K/N,TAB/K/N,P=PARA/K/N,STRIPCR/S,ADDCR/S

 @{" Grx        " LINK "grx"} RexxPortName CommandLine

